# WA Sender Tool

## Overview
A practical communication tool for WhatsApp and Email campaigns.
- Upload CSV/Excel files
- Batch send messages via WhatsApp or Email
- Track progress and statistics

## Files
- `page.tsx` - Main tool component (WA Sender interface)
- `globals.css` - Tool-specific Tailwind styles
- `layout.tsx` - Tool page layout

## Dependencies
- `xlsx` - Excel file parsing

## Note
This tool is completely isolated. To add a new tool:
1. Create `app/tools/new-tool/` folder
2. Add `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, and `globals.css` (if using Tailwind)
3. Update the navbar and sitemap to include the new tool route

Do NOT mix tool files with main site files.
